TY  - JOUR
TI  - The Covariance Matrices of Reduced-Form Coefficients and of Forecasts for a Structural Econometric Model
AU  - Goldberger, A. S.
AU  - Nagar, A. L.
AU  - Odeh, H. S.
AB  - [For a structural econometric model, we obtain formulas for the covariance matrix of the coefficients of the derived reduced-form system and for the covariance matrix of forecasts. A numerical illustration is provided.]
