TI  - The Stability of Dynamic Processes
AU  - Uzawa, Hirofumi
AB  - [In this paper the stability problem of general dynamic processes is investigated by the classical Lyapunov second method. The stability theorem will be applied to handle the price adjustment process in a competitive economy and generalize some of the results recently obtained by K. J. Arrow, H. K. Block, and L. Hurwicz.]
